HeliosX-Logger-Log4perl version 0.02
====================================

HeliosX::Logger::Log4perl extends the HeliosX::Logger class to provide 
a shim between HeliosX::ExtLoggerService and Log::Log4perl.  This 
allows Helios applications using HeliosX::ExtLoggerService to use 
Log4perl logging facilities.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Helios 2.00
  HeliosX::ExtLoggerService 0.02
  Log::Log4perl 


